descriptions: A rectangular aluminum foil tray with rounded corners, containing three oval-shaped, flat, yellowish objects arranged in a row.
A tall, cylindrical glass vase with a narrow neck and a flared rim, containing green stems and leaves.
A smooth, round, light pink ceramic bowl with a glossy finish and a slightly curved rim.
A brown spoon with a matte finish, featuring a rounded handle that tapers slightly towards the end and a flat, rectangular-shaped bowl with rounded edges.
A black microwave oven with a glossy finish, featuring a curved handle on the door, a digital control panel on the right side with multiple buttons, and a visible sticker on the top right corner.
The grill features a black, rectangular body with a matte finish, mounted on a sturdy, black metal frame with visible screws and a handle on the side.
A dark brown, rectangular-shaped bottle with a white label featuring a red and white logo at the top, the word "MUSTARD" in bold red letters, and an image of a mustard grinder with a mustard seed.
A tall, rectangular carton of milk with a white background and a prominent blue and red logo at the top, featuring the number "148" in large white font.
A modern chair with a curved, brown wooden backrest and seat, supported by a sleek, metallic frame with a single central leg that curves outward at the base.
A cluster of long, slender green leaves with pointed tips, arranged in a fan-like pattern, with some leaves overlapping each other.
A wooden chair with a curved, light brown backrest and a single, central metal support bar connecting the backrest to the seat.
A person wearing black pants and black shoes with white soles.
A transparent glass jar with a black screw-on lid, filled with a light brown powder.
A black, rectangular-shaped grill pan with a flat, slightly angled cooking surface and a raised, rounded edge.
A rectangular wooden table with a smooth surface and rounded edges, supported by four cylindrical legs that taper slightly towards the bottom.
A round, pale yellow potato with a smooth surface and a slightly irregular shape.
A single, oval-shaped potato slice with a smooth, pale yellow surface and a slightly darker, thin brown edge.
A round, golden-brown potato with a smooth, slightly shiny surface and a few shallow eyes scattered across its skin.
A rectangular, light gray box with a smooth surface and slightly rounded edges.
A white, rectangular power socket with a black plug inserted into it, featuring a black cable extending from the plug.
